<h1>SkålCon Registration Reminder!</h1>


<h2>Register for SkålCon!</h2>
<p>If you haven't done so already, please go onto
  <a href="https://pfs-registration.herokuapp.com/">MSP PFS Registration</a> and create your account. Once you have verified your email, you should click on the goldenrod "Register" button for SkålCon to register for the event! Please note that just creating an account on the MSP PFS Registration application does not register you for the event. Once you have registered for SkålCon, volunteers will be able to verify your paid status within 24 hours, and you will be able to select your sessions.</p>

<h2>GMs still needed!</h2>
<p>We can still use several GMs in all slots! If you are interested, please volunteer by adding your full name to a slot
  on the <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kKR-Z0WPtOpWJhYtGwaDQog29E6PhJ5CkvUD_QB6fqY/edit">GM Volunteer
  spreadsheet</a>. It is only through the generosity of our volunteer GMs that we can successful!</p>

<h2>Donations accepted!</h2>
<p>If you would like to donate something for either the silent auction or the raffle, please let us know by going to <a href="https://pfs-registration.herokuapp.com/contact">our contact page</a> and selecting 'I have something to donate!' in the dropdown. Someone will contact you to arrange for your donation.</p>

<p>Thank you for making this convention a success!</p>

<hr>
<p>SkålCon and MSP Pathfinders</p>
